

This IaaC was created to facilitate a deployment of an application on a server. An application uses a remote database 
(with private IP) as the app backend.

  The infrastructure created via this code contains:

  - VPC network and subnetwork (+ firewall rules);
  - Compute instance with static IP;
  - MySQL 5.7 instance with private IP;
  - MySQL 5.7 database and it`s user;
  - Private VPC connection to bind a compute instance with the MY_SQL database;
  - another infrastructure components.


